{"word":"extrañar","level":"B1","en":"to miss (someone/something, Argentine)","ru":"скучать (арг.)","de":"vermissen (arg.)","tr":"özlemek (Arj.)","examples":[{"es_ar":"Extraño mucho a mi familia.","en":"I miss my family a lot.","ru":"Я очень скучаю по семье.","de":"Ich vermisse meine Familie sehr.","tr":"Ailemi çok özlüyorum."},{"es_ar":"Voy a extrañar este lugar.","en":"I'm going to miss this place.","ru":"Я буду скучать по этому месту.","de":"Ich werde diesen Ort vermissen.","tr":"Bu yeri özleyeceğim."}]},
{"word":"enojado","level":"B1","en":"angry (Argentine)","ru":"злой, сердитый (арг.)","de":"wütend, verärgert (arg.)","tr":"kızgın (Arj.)","examples":[{"es_ar":"Está enojado conmigo por lo de ayer.","en":"He's angry with me about yesterday.","ru":"Он злится на меня из-за вчерашнего.","de":"Er ist wegen gestern wütend auf mich.","tr":"Dünkü olay yüzünden bana kızgın."},{"es_ar":"No te enojes, era una broma.","en":"Don't get angry, it was a joke.","ru":"Не злись, это была шутка.","de":"Sei nicht wütend, es war ein Scherz.","tr":"Kızma, şakaydı."}]},
{"word":"medio ambiente","level":"B1","en":"environment","ru":"окружающая среда","de":"Umwelt","tr":"çevre","examples":[{"es_ar":"Hay que cuidar el medio ambiente.","en":"We have to take care of the environment.","ru":"Нужно беречь окружающую среду.","de":"Wir müssen die Umwelt schützen.","tr":"Çevreyi korumalıyız."},{"es_ar":"La contaminación afecta el medio ambiente.","en":"Pollution affects the environment.","ru":"Загрязнение влияет на окружающую среду.","de":"Die Verschmutzung schadet der Umwelt.","tr":"Kirlilik çevreyi etkiler."}]},
{"word":"reciclar","level":"B1","en":"to recycle","ru":"перерабатывать","de":"recyceln","tr":"geri dönüştürmek","examples":[{"es_ar":"En casa reciclamos el plástico y el papel.","en":"At home we recycle plastic and paper.","ru":"Дома мы перерабатываем пластик и бумагу.","de":"Zu Hause recyceln wir Plastik und Papier.","tr":"Evde plastik ve kâğıdı geri dönüştürüyoruz."},{"es_ar":"Es importante reciclar la basura.","en":"It's important to recycle waste.","ru":"Важно перерабатывать мусор.","de":"Es ist wichtig, Müll zu recyceln.","tr":"Çöpü geri dönüştürmek önemli."}]},
{"word":"noticia","level":"B1","en":"news (item)","ru":"новость","de":"Nachricht","tr":"haber","examples":[{"es_ar":"Te tengo una buena noticia.","en":"I have good news for you.","ru":"У меня для тебя хорошая новость.","de":"Ich habe eine gute Nachricht für dich.","tr":"Sana iyi bir haberim var."},{"es_ar":"Leí la noticia en el diario.","en":"I read the news in the paper.","ru":"Я прочитал новость в газете.","de":"Ich habe die Nachricht in der Zeitung gelesen.","tr":"Haberi gazetede okudum."}]},
{"word":"red social","level":"B1","en":"social network","ru":"социальная сеть","de":"soziales Netzwerk","tr":"sosyal ağ","examples":[{"es_ar":"Paso demasiado tiempo en las redes sociales.","en":"I spend too much time on social media.","ru":"Я провожу слишком много времени в соцсетях.","de":"Ich verbringe zu viel Zeit in sozialen Netzwerken.","tr":"Sosyal ağlarda çok fazla vakit geçiriyorum."},{"es_ar":"Lo vi en las redes.","en":"I saw it on social media.","ru":"Я видел это в соцсетях.","de":"Ich habe es in den sozialen Netzwerken gesehen.","tr":"Onu sosyal medyada gördüm."}]},
{"word":"mensaje","level":"B1","en":"message","ru":"сообщение","de":"Nachricht","tr":"mesaj","examples":[{"es_ar":"Te mandé un mensaje hace un rato.","en":"I sent you a message a while ago.","ru":"Я отправил тебе сообщение недавно.","de":"Ich habe dir vorhin eine Nachricht geschickt.","tr":"Az önce sana mesaj attım."},{"es_ar":"No vi tu mensaje, perdón.","en":"I didn't see your message, sorry.","ru":"Я не видел твоё сообщение, извини.","de":"Ich habe deine Nachricht nicht gesehen, sorry.","tr":"Mesajını görmedim, pardon."}]},
{"word":"gobierno","level":"B1","en":"government","ru":"правительство","de":"Regierung","tr":"hükümet","examples":[{"es_ar":"El gobierno anunció nuevas medidas.","en":"The government announced new measures.","ru":"Правительство объявило новые меры.","de":"Die Regierung kündigte neue Maßnahmen an.","tr":"Hükümet yeni önlemler açıkladı."},{"es_ar":"Mucha gente está en contra del gobierno.","en":"Many people are against the government.","ru":"Многие против правительства.","de":"Viele Menschen sind gegen die Regierung.","tr":"Birçok insan hükümete karşı."}]},
{"word":"sociedad","level":"B1","en":"society","ru":"общество","de":"Gesellschaft","tr":"toplum","examples":[{"es_ar":"Es un tema que preocupa a toda la sociedad.","en":"It's an issue that worries the whole society.","ru":"Это вопрос, который волнует всё общество.","de":"Es ist ein Thema, das die ganze Gesellschaft beschäftigt.","tr":"Bu, tüm toplumu ilgilendiren bir konu."},{"es_ar":"La sociedad cambió mucho en los últimos años.","en":"Society has changed a lot in recent years.","ru":"Общество сильно изменилось за последние годы.","de":"Die Gesellschaft hat sich in den letzten Jahren stark verändert.","tr":"Toplum son yıllarda çok değişti."}]},
{"word":"importante","level":"B1","en":"important","ru":"важный","de":"wichtig","tr":"önemli","examples":[{"es_ar":"Es importante que llegues a horario.","en":"It's important that you arrive on time.","ru":"Важно, чтобы ты пришёл вовремя.","de":"Es ist wichtig, dass du pünktlich kommst.","tr":"Zamanında gelmen önemli."},{"es_ar":"Lo más importante es la salud.","en":"The most important thing is health.","ru":"Самое важное — это здоровье.","de":"Das Wichtigste ist die Gesundheit.","tr":"En önemli şey sağlık."}]},
{"word":"aunque","level":"B1","en":"although, even though","ru":"хотя","de":"obwohl","tr":"her ne kadar, -e rağmen","examples":[{"es_ar":"Aunque llueva, salimos igual.","en":"Even if it rains, we're still going out.","ru":"Даже если пойдёт дождь, мы всё равно выйдем.","de":"Auch wenn es regnet, gehen wir trotzdem raus.","tr":"Yağmur yağsa bile yine de çıkarız."},{"es_ar":"Fui aunque estaba cansado.","en":"I went even though I was tired.","ru":"Я пошёл, хотя устал.","de":"Ich ging, obwohl ich müde war.","tr":"Yorgun olsam da gittim."}]},
{"word":"quizás","level":"B1","en":"maybe, perhaps","ru":"может быть","de":"vielleicht","tr":"belki","examples":[{"es_ar":"Quizás vaya mañana, no sé.","en":"Maybe I'll go tomorrow, I don't know.","ru":"Может быть, пойду завтра, не знаю.","de":"Vielleicht gehe ich morgen, ich weiß nicht.","tr":"Belki yarın giderim, bilmiyorum."},{"es_ar":"Quizás tengas razón.","en":"Maybe you're right.","ru":"Может, ты и прав.","de":"Vielleicht hast du recht.","tr":"Belki haklısın."}],"syn":["tal vez"]},
{"word":"aprovechar","level":"B1","en":"to make the most of, take advantage of","ru":"воспользоваться","de":"nutzen, ausnutzen","tr":"değerlendirmek, fırsat bilmek","examples":[{"es_ar":"Aprovechá que está barato y comprá ahora.","en":"Take advantage of it being cheap and buy now.","ru":"Пользуйся тем, что дёшево, и покупай сейчас.","de":"Nutz es, dass es günstig ist, und kauf jetzt.","tr":"Ucuzken fırsatı değerlendir ve şimdi al."},{"es_ar":"Aproveché el finde largo para descansar.","en":"I made the most of the long weekend to rest.","ru":"Я использовал длинные выходные, чтобы отдохнуть.","de":"Ich nutzte das lange Wochenende zum Ausruhen.","tr":"Uzun hafta sonunu dinlenmek için değerlendirdim."}]},
{"word":"quilombo","level":"B1","en":"mess, chaos (Argentine, informal)","ru":"бардак, хаос (арг., разг.)","de":"Chaos, Durcheinander (arg., ugs.)","tr":"karmaşa, kargaşa (Arj., günlük)","examples":[{"es_ar":"Se armó un quilombo bárbaro en la oficina.","en":"A huge mess broke out at the office.","ru":"В офисе поднялся жуткий бардак.","de":"Im Büro brach ein Riesenchaos aus.","tr":"Ofiste büyük bir kargaşa çıktı."},{"es_ar":"Tengo la pieza hecha un quilombo.","en":"My room is a total mess.","ru":"У меня в комнате полный бардак.","de":"Mein Zimmer ist ein einziges Chaos.","tr":"Odam tam bir karmaşa."}],"syn":["lío","desastre"]},
{"word":"bárbaro","level":"B1","en":"great, awesome (Argentine, informal)","ru":"классно, отлично (арг., разг.)","de":"super, klasse (arg., ugs.)","tr":"harika, süper (Arj., günlük)","examples":[{"es_ar":"—Nos vemos a las ocho. —¡Bárbaro!","en":"—See you at eight. —Great!","ru":"—Увидимся в восемь. —Отлично!","de":"—Wir sehen uns um acht. —Super!","tr":"—Sekizde görüşürüz. —Harika!"},{"es_ar":"La pasamos bárbaro en la fiesta.","en":"We had an awesome time at the party.","ru":"Мы отлично провели время на вечеринке.","de":"Wir hatten eine super Zeit auf der Party.","tr":"Partide harika vakit geçirdik."}],"syn":["genial","copado"]},
{"word":"copado","level":"B1","en":"cool, great (Argentine, informal)","ru":"крутой, классный (арг., разг.)","de":"cool, toll (arg., ugs.)","tr":"havalı, güzel (Arj., günlük)","examples":[{"es_ar":"Ese recital estuvo re copado.","en":"That concert was super cool.","ru":"Тот концерт был очень классным.","de":"Das Konzert war echt cool.","tr":"O konser gerçekten havalıydı."},{"es_ar":"Tu amigo es muy copado.","en":"Your friend is really cool.","ru":"Твой друг очень классный.","de":"Dein Freund ist echt cool.","tr":"Arkadaşın çok havalı."}]},
{"word":"boludo","level":"B1","en":"dude/idiot (Argentine slang — friendly among friends, insulting to strangers)","ru":"чувак/дурак (арг. сленг — по-дружески среди своих, оскорбление к чужим)","de":"Alter/Idiot (arg. Slang — freundlich unter Freunden, beleidigend zu Fremden)","tr":"dostum/salak (Arj. argosu — arkadaşlar arası samimi, yabancıya hakaret)","examples":[{"es_ar":"Dale, boludo, no te enojes.","en":"Come on, dude, don't get mad. (friendly)","ru":"Да ладно, чувак, не злись. (по-дружески)","de":"Komm schon, Alter, sei nicht sauer. (freundlich)","tr":"Hadi dostum, kızma. (samimi)"},{"es_ar":"No seas boludo, prestá atención.","en":"Don't be dumb, pay attention.","ru":"Не будь дураком, будь внимателен.","de":"Sei nicht blöd, pass auf.","tr":"Salak olma, dikkat et."}]},
{"word":"aprender","level":"B1","en":"to learn","ru":"учить, учиться","de":"lernen","tr":"öğrenmek","examples":[{"es_ar":"Estoy aprendiendo a manejar.","en":"I'm learning to drive.","ru":"Я учусь водить.","de":"Ich lerne gerade fahren.","tr":"Araba sürmeyi öğreniyorum."},{"es_ar":"Aprendí mucho en este laburo.","en":"I learned a lot in this job.","ru":"Я многому научился на этой работе.","de":"Ich habe in diesem Job viel gelernt.","tr":"Bu işte çok şey öğrendim."}]},
{"word":"mejorar","level":"B1","en":"to improve, get better","ru":"улучшать(ся)","de":"verbessern, besser werden","tr":"iyileştirmek, iyileşmek","examples":[{"es_ar":"Quiero mejorar mi español.","en":"I want to improve my Spanish.","ru":"Я хочу улучшить свой испанский.","de":"Ich will mein Spanisch verbessern.","tr":"İspanyolcamı geliştirmek istiyorum."},{"es_ar":"El clima va a mejorar el fin de semana.","en":"The weather will improve over the weekend.","ru":"Погода улучшится к выходным.","de":"Das Wetter wird am Wochenende besser.","tr":"Hava hafta sonu düzelecek."}]}
